Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.44,0:01:29.93,staff,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(100,250)\a6}製作 ？ 秋月暮葉
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.30,0:01:23.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\a6}Sao Cabal 三月19日
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.89,0:01:33.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ha... chin
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.53,0:01:42.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,chin啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.50,0:01:44.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}沉迷的彈珠游戲
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.84,0:01:51.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“怎么看都是普通的石頭啊”
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.94,0:01:54.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你是這么想的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.92,0:02:01.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,認為這些石頭是普通石頭的想法 正是你的可悲之處
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.05,0:02:04.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種石頭叫Forca Pedra(力量之石)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.10,0:02:09.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,只要帶在身邊就能趕走惡運的奇跡之石
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.86,0:02:12.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,和一般的石頭可是大不相同的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.37,0:02:13.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,還有好東西
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.38,0:02:16.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的指甲垢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.17,0:02:20.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎湯后服下能開啟你的神通力
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.43,0:02:22.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 效果因人而異
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.50,0:02:24.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個人是什么人？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.92,0:02:27.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,神的使者哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.83,0:02:29.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.94,0:02:32.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么... 意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.99,0:02:35.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有椅子吧 做我大腿上
Dialogue: 0,0:02:35.62,0:02:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不必了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.50,0:02:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么啦 那副表情
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.35,0:02:44.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像正在看著小偷一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.39,0:02:47.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.75,0:02:49.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.34,0:02:52.66,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,人的表情可不是什么天生的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.81,0:02:57.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽好 人的臉是顯示人體能量的計量器
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.84,0:03:00.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身上有很多惡氣
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.95,0:03:02.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有那么壞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.42,0:03:05.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,已經不是壞不壞的問題了 糟糕透了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.34,0:03:06.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么辦啊 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.88,0:03:08.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的情況糟透了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.89,0:03:13.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過 會怎樣啊 如果能夠看見未來
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.93,0:03:17.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,如果能回避將要發生的災難
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,非常好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.72,0:03:20.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能辦得到嗎 大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.21,0:03:24.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有點貴哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:30.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.17,0:03:32.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這個城市里哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.86,0:03:36.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.72,0:03:38.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,突然來感覺了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.63,0:03:42.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太棒了！ 是不是指甲垢的功效啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.74,0:03:45.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你相信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.37,0:03:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那可是真家伙(指甲垢)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.90,0:03:49.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接著 Forca Pedra
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.12,0:03:53.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.38,0:04:07.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.95,0:04:11.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我翻白眼可不是在演戲 是在通靈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.37,0:04:15.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的靈魂離開了肉體
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.04,0:04:21.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,高高飛起 現在我身處宇宙之中
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.86,0:04:24.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見時間之流 是通往未來的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.74,0:04:26.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我看到你了 女人！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.55,0:04:27.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.44,0:04:29.21,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是“我”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.29,0:04:30.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在尋找著什么
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.59,0:04:31.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.64,0:04:33.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:33.92,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,男人？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.10,0:04:35.44,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 是男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.53,0:04:37.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是肖像畫
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.54,0:04:38.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,肖像畫？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.89,0:04:42.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你找到了 是你要找的男人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.49,0:04:43.61,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很幸福
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.75,0:04:48.41,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有兩個孩子 建立了幸福的家庭
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.42,0:04:49.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么時候？在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.93,0:04:55.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不久的將來 踏踏實實的努力會結出碩果
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.10,0:04:56.42,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,少女啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.71,0:05:00.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,看到了 注意你的右腳！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.35,0:05:04.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,微小的不幸招致巨大的不幸
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.92,0:05:09.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,放棄吧！ 不要去追逃走的人！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.15,0:05:12.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！ 山！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.81,0:05:14.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要爬！ 槍聲！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.19,0:05:16.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見海
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.86,0:05:20.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的 會死的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.43,0:05:25.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.76,0:05:29.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大媽 Forca Pedra有效果嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.46,0:05:33.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有效 非常有效
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.46,0:05:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能救她嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.52,0:05:35.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.51,0:05:38.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,她會得救嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.07,0:05:40.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,當然
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.13,0:05:42.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這種東西我才不要呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:44.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,指甲垢一起買了如何？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.17,0:05:47.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開心套餐 特別優惠20%哦
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.67,0:05:51.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不要 這種東西
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.82,0:05:57.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 喂
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.23,0:05:58.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,要去哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.57,0:06:01.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,請自便吧 我不管你了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.06,0:06:05.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,狗屎...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.55,0:06:09.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不正是右腳吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.92,0:06:11.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 (占卜)是真家伙吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.47,0:06:12.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話就過來吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.90,0:06:14.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.94,0:06:21.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}Hotel Venus:維納斯旅館
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.36,0:06:24.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin 要出去了
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.95,0:06:26.76,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不去
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.76,0:06:33.04,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫... 我回來之前你一步也不許出房門哦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.41,0:06:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 你的回答呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.49,0:06:36.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.23,0:07:10.83,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喲 Hatchin
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:14.82,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你回來啦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.56,0:07:20.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎... 么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.07,0:07:23.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個 是Hiroshi哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.08,0:07:30.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi... 嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.82,0:07:32.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.41,0:07:35.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有個畫畫的 我請他幫了個忙 就是這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.46,0:07:36.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我吃了一驚
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.22,0:07:39.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,啊 還有這個
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.73,0:07:41.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,穿上試試
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.16,0:07:44.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.76,0:07:48.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么 是我的愛啊 是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.37,0:07:52.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是這個 是鞋 怎么回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.79,0:07:54.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,擺在那里...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.35,0:07:55.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.59,0:07:56.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,鞋店
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:59.08,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這是你為我買的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.99,0:08:01.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.13,0:08:02.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,偷的嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.63,0:08:08.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 別說的這么難聽
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.21,0:08:09.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,“請試穿一下吧”
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:13.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是店員拿給我的...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.11,0:08:30.66,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(200,200)\pos(470,360)}三月20日
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.88,0:08:38.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.50,0:08:58.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了 那個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.06,0:09:00.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.12,0:09:06.48,comment,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}新設計
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.71,0:09:16.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}招聘啟事
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.16,0:09:19.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.36,0:09:21.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.87,0:09:24.46,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我想工作 打工
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.63,0:09:25.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這里不需要小孩！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.19,0:09:27.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會拼命工作的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.57,0:09:30.69,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,所有的人開始都是這么說的 包括大人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.84,0:09:32.98,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是沒人能堅持下來
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.11,0:09:34.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,知道為什么嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.64,0:09:36.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我Ram Yin非常能干
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.28,0:09:38.90,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了的話 回去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.81,0:09:41.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不明白！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.95,0:09:45.89,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為我也可能很能干啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.27,0:09:48.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,試都沒試你憑什么斷定
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.07,0:09:50.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不回去
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.02,0:09:56.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫什么名字？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.38,0:09:57.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Morenos...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.94,0:09:58.64,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.90,0:10:00.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana Morehana？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.35,0:10:01.58,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.70,0:10:02.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,給我看身份證
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.87,0:10:03.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.70,0:10:05.13,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,開什么玩笑！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.46,0:10:09.31,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,等等
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.17,0:10:12.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你 為什么不穿鞋？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.85,0:10:16.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為還沒有付錢 工作賺錢后再去買
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.84,0:10:25.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你剛才說的好
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.45,0:10:27.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的 我沒有去試
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.43,0:10:30.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,因為你是小孩 工資減半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.34,0:10:32.09,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒有身份證 再減一半
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:34.30,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好好干的話 1天給你10Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.96,0:10:38.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是我要試用你 所以今天不給工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.74,0:10:41.78,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你身份可疑 所以明天也不給工錢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.01,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,以后每天10Arca
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.71,0:10:44.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.96,0:10:46.03,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了嗎 Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.03,0:10:50.79,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 請不要叫我Hana
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.21,0:10:52.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.52,0:10:54.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你叫Hana 我叫Ram
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.64,0:10:56.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我不喜歡...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.10,0:11:00.59,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,被人叫Hana的時候 會想起那些討厭的人的臉
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.69,0:11:04.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,女人就是羅嗦！ 那么叫你什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.47,0:11:07.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hatchin...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.29,0:11:08.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好的 Hachin
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.58,0:11:09.45,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hachin？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.67,0:11:11.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,菜單要背下來
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.59,0:11:14.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,然后看到我這樣做 就是警戒的暗號 不要忘了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.94,0:11:16.37,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 警戒是什么意思...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:19.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,五位客人光臨 要吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.61,0:11:35.67,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔 認識這家伙嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.19,0:11:37.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hiroshi Morenos
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.83,0:11:41.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不 不認識啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.35,0:11:44.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大叔能再看一下嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.72,0:11:47.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,就當是在看我的胸脯啦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.25,0:11:48.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.22,0:11:52.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那么這張怎么樣？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.24,0:11:54.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個女孩
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.05,0:12:02.95,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:11.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.55,0:12:19.00,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么回事！ 根本不像是父女嘛！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.27,0:12:30.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別讓人替你擔心啊 這個家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.09,0:12:32.07,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,去哪里了？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.04,0:12:40.32,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,煎餃三份
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.24,0:12:44.24,portugal,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\a1\fad(200,200)}超級飯店 三月21日
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.94,0:13:01.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,暗號？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.40,0:13:10.12,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別跑！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.86,0:13:14.02,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,超級飯店 別想吃霸王餐！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.11,0:13:15.38,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你的臉我記住了！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.56,0:13:18.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,讓老子用功夫送你下地獄！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.49,0:13:28.25,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也有個Hatchin這么大的女兒
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.57,0:13:30.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過更能干
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:33.55,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 從沒失敗過
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.96,0:13:35.87,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.93,0:13:39.86,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,有你和沒你都一樣 沒用的家伙
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.79,0:13:43.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不過我很溫柔 還會試用你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.92,0:13:45.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明天還是沒有工錢哦
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.31,0:13:48.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么哼哼哈哈的！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.37,0:13:50.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 可惡！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.10,0:13:53.51,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點也不溫柔！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.41,0:14:17.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我鼓起干勁了 會像變了個人一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.38,0:14:26.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦 這個家伙...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.96,0:14:30.22,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,好像在什么地方見過
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.23,0:14:32.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在哪里？ 在哪里見過？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.56,0:14:33.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,拜托了！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.28,0:14:37.17,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你想一想啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.31,0:14:41.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那邊貧民區外圍的一間房子
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.78,0:14:42.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝了 大叔
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.02,0:14:46.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你真是個好男人
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.59,0:15:03.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我去追！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,別去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.50,0:15:20.81,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你這個家伙 再跟過來 就殺了你
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.89,0:15:22.71,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,羅嗦！ 付錢！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.52,0:15:29.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我的... 鞋！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.97,0:15:45.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要去！
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.51,0:15:50.23,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不要爬山！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.31,0:16:10.14,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:25.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在那里！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.38,0:16:34.43,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可以看見海
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.55,0:16:41.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,會死的！ 會死的！ 會死！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.87,0:16:52.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,找到了！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.99,0:16:54.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.75,0:17:17.49,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,奇跡之石？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.26,0:17:28.84,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 沒事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.07,0:17:52.50,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,臭小鬼！ 要我放火燒了你的鳥窩頭嗎！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.73,0:17:56.28,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么嘛 明明是你沖過來的吧
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.95,0:17:59.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你丫 是Hatchin嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.00,0:18:03.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊？ 穿成這樣
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.48,0:18:05.96,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,霸王餐...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.06,0:18:06.74,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你做了？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.74,0:18:07.40,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.89,0:18:08.77,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 大媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.86,0:18:10.34,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,礙事 閃開！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.32,0:18:11.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大媽？！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.16,0:18:15.88,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,聽不見嗎 大媽！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:18.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,想讓我在你的大咪咪上開個洞嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.43,0:18:22.57,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你以為你在和誰說話？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.77,0:18:24.15,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,搞什么！ 你這個...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.73,0:18:25.62,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.78,0:18:28.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我聽不見！ 你剛才在說什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.92,0:18:29.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,痛痛痛...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.33,0:18:30.27,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么大媽
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.51,0:18:39.48,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 說話啊！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.71,0:18:46.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,大... 大姐姐
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:50.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.22,0:18:53.18,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,可惡！ 給我記住！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.76,0:18:58.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在干什么啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.47,0:19:01.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,沒什么
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.44,0:19:03.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你在做什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.97,0:19:08.05,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,在這里 Hiroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.88,0:19:34.63,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,您是哪位？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.82,0:19:39.16,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,喂 老公！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.44,0:19:40.10,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.11,0:19:53.29,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個... 爸爸...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.20,0:19:54.99,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,怎么了？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.21,0:19:58.20,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是Hiroshi吧 是爸爸吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.11,0:19:58.72,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不是
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.15,0:20:02.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,為什么？ 很像啊 非常像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.12,0:20:07.26,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我說過了 不是的 不是Hiroshi啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.30,0:20:13.80,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都不像
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.79,0:20:17.60,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,回去了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:19.35,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真的不是嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.41,0:20:21.94,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真煩人！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.38,0:20:25.33,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來那張肖像畫真的像他本人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.28,0:20:28.47,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,像不像都無所謂吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.72,0:20:31.11,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是個帥哥的事實又不會變
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.59,0:20:34.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來 都是那個占卜的老太婆不好
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.70,0:20:36.56,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,一點都沒有預測中
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.64,0:20:38.85,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么踏實的努力啊 傻瓜嗎
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.53,0:20:43.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,預測中了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.79,0:20:44.68,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,什么地方？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.79,0:20:47.52,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你不是沒死嗎 活蹦亂跳的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.83,0:20:49.24,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那個死老太婆 下地獄去吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.36,0:20:50.53,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次讓我再遇見 要好好揍她一頓
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.78,0:20:51.91,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不許攔著我哦
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.41,0:20:57.70,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,結果 除了肖像畫之外
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.06,0:20:59.75,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我覺得占卜都預測中了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.86,0:21:05.19,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,但是如果真的能在這里見到父親的話
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.67,0:21:08.73,*Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我會是怎樣的表情啊
